  - nodeID: WHERE1
    nodeType: 0
    npcText: We're a little bit south of the capital, Arcanum and few miles from
      the small town of Treason. Arcanum isn't really the same anymore.
    editorPosition: {x: 850, y: -325}
    choices:
    - playerText: Why isn't it the same?
      nextNodeID: MAGES1
      closesDialogue: 0
      opensTrade: 0
      startsQuest: 0
      completesQuest: 0
      questToStart: {fileID: 0}
      questToCompleteID: 
