      requiredReadyToTurnInQuestID: 
  - nodeID: MAGES1
    nodeType: 0
    npcText: The damn.. magocracy - all of them are magic obsessed, knowledge rich,
      introverted assholes.
    editorPosition: {x: 1700, y: -325}
    choices:
    - playerText: Why isn't it the same?
      nextNodeID: MAGES2
      closesDialogue: 1
      opensTrade: 0
      startsQuest: 0
      completesQuest: 0
      questToStart: {fileID: 0}
      questToCompleteID: 
      requiredCompletedQuestID: 
      requiredReadyToTurnInQuestID: 
  - nodeID: QUEST1
    nodeType: 0
    npcText: Their seems to be some weird boney fellas that have been roaming these
      woods lately. Don't want some random lumber jack getting killed... take care
      of them for me?
    editorPosition: {x: 850, y: 325}
    choices:
    - playerText: Sure!
      nextNodeID: QUEST2
      closesDialogue: 0
      opensTrade: 0
      startsQuest: 1
      completesQuest: 0
      questToStart: {fileID: 11400000, guid: d7d629b859a0ebf41afed0a8aae2cd8d, type: 2}
      questToCompleteID: 
      requiredCompletedQuestID: 
      requiredReadyToTurnInQuestID: 
  - nodeID: QUEST2
    nodeType: 0
    npcText: Amazing thank you so much. Come back after killing a few of them and
